  "detailed_description": "Hovership Havoc is a sci-fi twin stick shooter with 3rd person boss battles. Blast through rooms of a futuristic robotic factory filled with robot enemies. Equip your Hovership with randomly dropped abilities and upgrade your stats during and before each playthrough.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Top Down Action</h2><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/872040/extras/topdown.gif?t=1555096799\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Third Person Boss Battles</h2><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/872040/extras/thirdperson.gif?t=1555096799\" ><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Randomly generated levels with 100s of combinations of rooms and enemy spawn patterns to ensure no two playthroughs are ever the same<br></li><li>4 playable Hoverships, each with their own unique main weapon and stats for completely different play styles<br></li><li>Giant robotic boss battles that take place in a 3rd person perspective instead of top down<br></li><li>30+ Hovership sci-fi abilities such as nanobots, drones, missiles, lasers, shields, and more<br></li><li>15+ Robotic enemy types with their own attack styles and AI<br></li><li>Collect ORBs to upgrade your hovership stats and abilities<br></li><li>Permanent progression for each hovership between playthroughs<br></li><li>Supports keyboard and mouse or controller input<br></li><li>3 Different futuristic sci-fi robotic factory environments</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Join us on Discord!</h2><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://discord.gg/5uQCN4J\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >https://discord.gg/5uQCN4J</a>",
